                                        <h2 class="entry-title">4. Managing Your Personal Information With Us</h2>
                                        <p>You control the personal data you share with us. You can access or rectify this data at any time. You can also deactivate your account. We also provide you tools to object, restrict, or withdraw consent where applicable
                                            for the use of data you have provided to Fidle. And we make the data you shared through our services portable and provide easy ways for you to contact us. Please note, to help protect your privacy and maintain
