                                        <p><strong>REACTIONS:</strong> fidle power can be used to tip (by tip; we mean ability of user to motivated and encourage of content creator, other task, especially during live streams.</p>

                                        <h2 class="entry-title">WHERE TO GET FIDLE POWER</h2>
